IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User anand.tk.03@gmail.com
PassCmd "gpg --quiet --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty --decrypt ~/Documents/.authinfo.gpg | awk '/machine imap.gmail.com/{print \$6}' | tr -d '\n'"
TLSType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt
AuthMechs LOGIN

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/email/gmail/
Inbox ~/email/gmail/Inbox

# With mbsync 1.4.0 and later: Use 'Far' instead of 'Master', and
# 'Near' instead of 'Slave'.
Channel gmail
Far :gmail-remote:
Near :gmail-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
SyncState *


IMAPAccount imperial
Host outlook.office365.com
Port 993
User st621@ic.ac.uk
PassCmd "imperial-oauth2"
AuthMechs XOAUTH2
TLSType IMAPS

IMAPStore imperial-remote
Account imperial

MaildirStore imperial-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/email/imperial/
Inbox ~/email/imperial/inbox

Channel imperial
Far :imperial-remote:
Near :imperial-local:
Patterns * !"Conversation History" !Calendar !Clutter
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
